      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Measurement contract\n- Compare **success-only end-to-end RPS and p99**. Fast sold-out or duplicate responses must not make a strategy look faster.\n- With the current 15 s Prometheus scrape interval, run each measured variant for **at least 2–5 minutes**. The k6 JSON remains the exact client-side result.\n- Run one coupon campaign/variant at a time and pin the exact time range. Prometheus `increase()` values and histogram quantiles are estimates; verify final Redis/DB invariants separately.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "13.1.0",
      "title": "How to read this dashboard",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Headline throughput comparison. Only final successful issuances are included.",
      "fieldConfig": {
